The John Dory’s crew in Nelspruit is ready to roll again.  With great Wednesday sushi specials and platters that the entire family can enjoy, don’t miss out on the best quality sushi made from the freshest ingredients. On Wednesday’s you can enjoy 26 pieces of sushi when you order a Maritime Platter (18 pieces) and  get a  free Two Oceans sushi platter (8 pieces).    1. Call on 013 757 0972 or 078 827 6253. 2. Download the Mr D Food App, select JD’s Nelspruit. Delivery takes place between 11:00 and 18:00.   